  "body": "PAUSE Phase E. Director ratified substantial orgdef substrate-shape change minutes ago: orgdefs become .opencatalog (atomic transportable bundles with positions + jobs as items) instead of .openthing (single org artifact + separate job files). This obsoletes E1's current target shape. Refactoring later costs more than pausing now. Net effect when SCHEMA v1.0.0 lands: Phase E gets simpler (one artifact type to ingest; jobs become local items; simpler export). Suggested: branch current work, pause main-line, wait for proposal+decision (in flight, hours-not-days), refactor against new target. Full context in companion .body.md.",
